data.title: February 2023 Student-Athlete of the Month: Paul Nguyen
data.text:
Paul Nguyen, a sophomore on Seguin High School’s swimming team, has been selected as the City of Arlington’s Student-Athlete of the Month for February 2023.

With a second place finish in the 50-meter freestyle at Regionals, Nguyen was the only Arlington ISD student-athlete to qualify for the UIL State Swim Meet in Austin.

“He’s a leader in the water,” said Tony Tullbane, Seguin Head Swimming Coach. “As a teammate, one of the greatest things he does is brings it every day.”

Nguyen, whose favorite subject is Math, plans on majoring in engineering after he graduates.

You can learn more about Arlington ISD’s athletic programs across the school district by clicking here.

Congratulations to Paul for being this month’s honoree!
